      "message": "I see, this is about this case:\nmessage A {\n  message C {\n  }\n  C c \u003d 1;\n}\nmessage B {\n  message C {\n  }\n  C c \u003d 1;\n}\nIn which case I agree that A.C !\u003d B.C.",
